eone asks about end-of-term hardware value. We give you a cleaner answer.\n\nIt''s meant to make the deal easier to underwrite — a cleaner IC story, better recovery assumptions, more confidence to deploy. Not add complexity.\n\nWould a 20-minute call with our founders be useful? We can show you how it fits the credit box.\n\nJosh Augustine\nCorgi\ncorgi.xyz"}','cold_intro_lender','draft','2026-03-21 02:40:08',NULL,'a',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
